body_html:
Thanks for the report. But as you reported, this issue seems to be resolved with newer TF versions.
As 1.0 is now older than 7 months, we will not patch the release to fix this bug in 1.0.

Thank you very much for your report, and please let us know if you see this error in1.4 release
